text: Barßel is a municipality in Cloppenburg, in Lower Saxony, Germany. ==Division of the municipality== Barßel has 13 districts: * Barßel * Barßelermoor * Carolinenhof * Elisabethfehn * Harkebrügge * Lohe * Loher-Ostmark * Loher- Westmark * Neuland * Neulohe * Osterhausen * Reekenfeld * Roggenberg ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Cloppenburg (district)
